{"tid":1758770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（傳真社）觀塘選區發現東區的已蓋印選票","createTime":"2019-11-27T09:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T09:25:13.000Z","uid":154277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"deec18a0f8c93df5ddd734dbcdfd1ce14a3added","tid":1758770,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"【區選】觀塘安利選區迦密梁省德學校票站(J1001)點票時，發現一張來自東區翡翠選區(C14)的已蓋印選票。<br />\n安利選區兩名參選人引述票站主任解釋是「印刷錯誤」，不過票站主任同時透露，撇除該「港島票」，選票存根數目與收回的選票數目相符。傳真社就此向選舉事務處查詢，至截稿時未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n足本報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2pQKkpI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pQKkpI&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=4830f9a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2pQKkpI</a>"},{"pid":"fe1b5bb05d7453e33b33017e7f13e30f8be7ac46","tid":1758770,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:18:28.000Z","msg":"聽晚愛丁堡廣場見"},{"pid":"02aec3fea13eb3a1a6f179a22c9dff20c5ea5f65","tid":1758770,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:19:06.000Z","msg":"１２０８民陣遊行"},{"pid":"d4ae6bb6c6f8e30c073d09edbc259207624f966f","tid":1758770,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:19:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8510387154320e7b3c3277dd24a5e3091db9b5e0","tid":1758770,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"諗下都知無可能...<br />\n<br />\n全機械化自動打印<br />\n<br />\n前後頁選票都係啱 得呢張錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457d99d52c2038e7fd0592488a959efea6152dfa","tid":1758770,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:20:55.000Z","msg":"政府今次最大既失誤就係出術出得唔夠多"},{"pid":"9ea08015bb4b581951edbb6dc44e2619f8c8eb5d","tid":1758770,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}